WEBVTT

00:01:30.811 --> 00:01:34.050
Quickly, my brother and his wife
went into a fearsome blame game,

00:01:35.348 --> 00:01:36.637
and it got messy.

00:01:37.709 --> 00:01:42.589
I vacillated between therapist
and pissed-off sister.

00:01:44.029 --> 00:01:46.092
I wanted them to be better than this.

00:01:46.500 --> 00:01:49.370
"Come on, you two. Get your shit together.

00:01:50.025 --> 00:01:51.531
You're parents.

00:01:51.555 --> 00:01:53.920
Grow up and buck up."

00:01:56.280 --> 00:01:58.801
After we left, I called my mom,